title: Prototype 1
description: Now, as the Romance Writers of America reckons with its history of racism, will she finally get her due?

title: Prototype 2
description: That voice matches an official photograph from her earlier days, when she was a star editor of romance novels at Dell, then a division of Doubleday, in New York.

title: Prototype 3
description: Stephens is 87 now, under self-imposed lockdown in one of those amenity-rich mid-rise apartment complexes that have sprouted all over Houston, this one just north of Hermann Park, in the Binz area.
